{"tid":1079093,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[數學邏輯?]打工仔你知唔知？有13個月糧唔係天大福利","createTime":"2019-03-26T16:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T17:49:37.000Z","uid":35143,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44e7a020a6cf9b686c7bd15f98e986330eb680f2","tid":1079093,"uid":35143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一年有52個星期！</span></span></strong><br />\n為甚麼會這樣說呢？原因十分簡單，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我們每個月都有4個星期，一年就共有48個星期</span></strong>。說到這裡大家都可能發現了問題了，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為一年共有52個星期呀</strong></span>！52個星期減48個星期等於4個星期，亦即是1個月呀，所以年尾出花紅是13個月的薪水，根本是你這一年來的應得的薪金。<br />\n<br />\n我想問上面講既野係咪岩, 點解我睇落硬係覺得有d問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbd965580a863538f8f5490823530015dde91fe","tid":1079093,"uid":35143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nmplus.hk/543052/social-buzz/13%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B3%A7-%E8%8A%B1%E7%B4%85-%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2F543052%2Fsocial-buzz%2F13%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25B3%25A7-%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25B4%2585-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%2F&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5ZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=e6c2f910\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nmplus.hk/543052/social-buzz/13%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B3%A7-%E8%8A%B1%E7%B4%85-%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94/</a><br />\n<br />\n補link"},{"pid":"1e86fc60276a885306d8dcdaac84f5e7e5bceb4a","tid":1079093,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"香港勞工不嬲世界級低賤"},{"pid":"7deb96342dd14fc4dd36c251398fc9fcde5507f5","tid":1079093,"uid":58254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"每月得28日??<img src=